replies.content:
I am also busy with a T-shirt campaign and will release it's pro's and con's soon. It's all about the message guys.
We have very funky prints and people want something funny and fresh. These T-shirts are a bit dull. I would suggest you add a little humor to the design or something serious like, &lt;&lt; Bitcoin takes Money digital &gt;&gt;
It's crazy how much stock you have to carry for all the sizes, or do you manufacture on order? We only do the local markets and nothing online, because this is still a kids project from home. &lt; Entrepreneurs Day &gt;

